predict_classifier

Source: R/clinical_classifier.R
predict_classifier.Rd

This function uses the model trained with *train_classifier_model* to predict new samples.

Usage

predict_classifier(
  fcd,
  input_type,
  data_slot,
  sample_names = "expfcs_filename",
  model_object,
  seed
)

Arguments

fcd

flowframe object.

input_type

data to use.

data_slot

name of the data slot to use.

sample_names

Column name of the metadata table containing the file names.

model_object

flowframe object with the stored classifier model.

seed

seed to be used for the analysis.

Value

predict_classifier

Details

Predict Clinical Classifier
